$interpreted: Nolva: Who...are you guys?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Wait, you don't know NEKO!?
Nolva: ...I don't...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: You serious!? NEKO is like, SUPER famous, you know!!!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Then, you should at least know this person, right!?
PAFF: ...Me?
Nolva: I...don't know her either...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: OH MY GOD, you don't know her AND you don't know NEKO!? Are you really from Node 08? How old are you?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: From your appearance, you're at most in your twenties. How is it possible that you don't recognize us at all...
Nolva: Umm, about that, I'm actually 35 years old...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: !!!...You're kidding! How the heck...What do you use to take care of your skin!?
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Eh...wait a sec; then it might actually be possible for you to not know us. After all, you're not our target audience...you're too old...
Nolva: A-although I don't understand what you're talking about...I don't think I can refute anything...
Nolva: ...*sniff*...

PAFF: Umm, hello. I...my name is PAFF...
Do...do you know where we are now?
PAFF: I should be at the venue doing a rehearsal for my performance right now...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: NEKO too! I was just about to start streaming!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Ah, could it be, that we got kidnapped by fans who are kinda nuts?
Nolva: Kidnapped!? All of you are...
Nora: Just call me Nora.

Nolva: Greetings. My name is Nolva Carpenter...
Nora, are you the same as those two?
Nora: ...More or less.  I was already with them when I woke up. The first things I saw were the scattered wood splinters and you lying on the floor.
Nora: If you know what place this is, please tell us.
Nolva: This place? Probably somewhere along the Atlas border.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Atlas? Never heard of it. Is it in Node 08?
PAFF: I'm not sure. Sister never mentioned it...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Nobody's asking you. You're a super idol. There's no way you'd know about this kind of pointless crap.
Nora: ...This location doesn't exist in Node 03 either.
Nora: Miss Nolva, are you certain you haven't misspoken?
Nolva: Of course! My home is in the nearby Paradise Prairie. I accidentally wandered into this place while looking for ingredients.
Nolva: Ah, right. I also ran into these marionette monsters...
PAFF: M-marionette monsters?
Nolva: Yes. Even though I don't remember very clearly, I think they attacked me first, then my monster friend helped me drive them away...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: ...NEKO understands now. This is your character!
Nolva: Character?

NEKO#ΦωΦ: Muu~ It certainly is a very unique character design.
However, that monster stuff is too much. We're not in an Isekai, ya know.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Besides, the eccentric weirdo route is not exactly popular these days. Not to mention you're already 35...
Nolva: Umm, I don't understand what you're talking about...
NEKO#ΦωΦ: Aww, no need to be shy. NEKO knows this sort of feeling very~ well.
NEKO#ΦωΦ: How about this, once NEKO gets home I'll find you on iM. Then I'll tell you the secret of how to become an uber-famous streamer in no time...
Nora: ...Anyway, let's leave this room first.
Nora: There's a ray of light over there. Seems to be the exit.
PAFF: You're right. It seems to be...a door!
NEKO#ΦωΦ: NEKO's going home~ Bye-bye, weird girl~
PAFF: Uh, um, we should also...
Nolva: ...Okay.
